{"tid":1896443,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"撐警張智霖fb蒲頭遭圍攻","createTime":"2020-02-25T06:32:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T06:32:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f7bba7467f3c77af8bbc8a85b9a6bea66207bec5","tid":1896443,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T06:32:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200225/6N6QGXVWNOEYSWVEFMNFDQTD6M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200225%2F6N6QGXVWNOEYSWVEFMNFDQTD6M%2F&d=2snho0MtSZbn8sjHWbtmpRVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=a839102d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200225%2F6N6QGXVWNOEYSWVEFMNFDQTD6M%2F&h=3db7472a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200225/6N6QGXVWNOEYSWVEFMNFDQTD6M/</a><br />\n<br />\n撐警張智霖fb蒲頭遭圍攻<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n張智霖（Chilam）早前參與警務處處長鄧炳強與晨曦明星足球隊飯局後，一家人連太太袁詠儀（靚靚）和囝囝張慕童（魔童）都被網民洗版鬧爆。Chilam前晚在fb貼蘭花相，留言：「祝大家身體健康。」引來逾二千留言，一半是揶揄Chilam，但亦有忠粉撐他。<br />\n<br />\n對於Chilam的祝福，有網友鬧︰「一個支持打香港小朋友嘅人，唔慌好人」、「免啦，受唔起！不如閣下為貴兒子積多啲福仲好啦！」又有人寸爆他可能累全家︰「有無自我隔離14日，一個累全家，祝君好，希望沒有傳染到吧，一變四，四變十二」，網民更表示罷買他代言的產品。但亦有忠粉撐偶像︰「惡毒言語不需要理會」。<br />\n<br />\n撰文︰祖李<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200225/large/1582552664_20fa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200225%2Flarge%2F1582552664_20fa.jpg&h=79f568f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早前參與撐警無罩宴的張智霖（左），昨日在fb蒲頭，即遭網民留言鬧爆。"}]}